ROBERT, by the grace of God King of Scots, to all good men of his whole land, clergy and lasty, greeting: Know ye that we have given, granted, and by this our present charter have confirmed to our beloved and faithful Adam For-ster, for his faithful service done to us, ten merks os sterlings from our fermes of the Burgh of Edinburgh, which J anet Stury now receives for the time of her life.
